io.smudgr.api

Class ApiMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.smudgr.api.ApiMessage

  • public class ApiMessage
extends java.lang.Object
    The ApiMessage class represents a packet of information for communicating with the API.

    Instances are backed by a JSONObject, so this class can be thought of as having key:value pairs and nested information.
